    "description": "Instamojo International Enterprises is actively seeking a talented and motivated Investment Banker to join our dynamic team in Madurai. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Instamojo International Enterprises:\nInstamojo International Enterprises is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Madurai, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Instamojo International Enterprises!",
